snippet.title: Psych – A Modern Horror Story Game | Teaser 2021
snippet.description:
Add Psych to your wishlist – https://store.steampowered.com/app/1404660/Psych

Experience the story of Alexander Green and find out what happened on the day of the accident. Follow the development of Alex, solve puzzles around the event and try not to fall into madness.

Support the project on Kickstarter – https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/mediatale/psych-a-modern-horror-game

Social Media
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mediataleat
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MediaTaleAT

Website: https://games.mediatale.at

Psych is a modern horror story game which will be released in 2021 on Steam
